column5: Like to wish the WC followers a Happy New Year.
Same to you prov1800. Sounds like you folks have good ice and now decent snow on the ground? Be safe and leave a few for the rest of us. Pooch
Got enough snow but will get more and had 16" of ice on cedar last weekend.

Boarding for the 2020 flight is announced! Carry only the best memories of 2019 in your luggage ... leave lost moments to bad times. The duration of your trip will be exactly 12 months. Your next stopovers are: Health, Love, Joy, Harmony, Prosperity and Peace. The Captain offers you the following menu, served during the flight: Friendship cocktail Supreme of good health Gratin of prosperity Excellent news set Success salad Happiness log All accompanied by bursts of laughter. Have a good and pleasant trip on flight 2020 but don't forget your friends who are currently fighting a sickness or a disease. Happy New Years everyone!!
Here's to health and happiness for all of you in 2020. Sent from my iPhone using Tapatalk
Happy New Year to all. May your achievements exceed your expectations!! Bill
